creditline: Gift of Fay M. Gallus and Richard M. Sweet
description: black and white double exposure image of two faces of the same man (Muhammed Ali). The face on the left of the composition has an open mouth and the person's gaze is directed to the right. The face on the right of the composition has a closed, pursed mouthand the person's gaze is directed to the left.
signed: recto, BR in black ink: [copyright] Tyrone Dukes
title: Untitled (Portrait of Muhammed Ali)
